{"tid":2038783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒 NEXT] 請求世界各專業組織拒絕承認香港專業資格","createTime":"2020-05-27T17:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T18:20:23.000Z","uid":147226,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c36d33d865c57baac28208a7eb5b7dc1c6530fe3","tid":2038783,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"例子：香港工程師學會，係同超過 20 個世界各地嘅組織有「專業資格互認協議」 ，即係只要取得香港嘅專業資格，就可以免卻當地考牌制度，攞到當地專業資格<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkie.org.hk/zh-hant/quali/reciprocal_agreement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkie.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fquali%2Freciprocal_agreement%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32QomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=846fe7a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkie.org.hk/zh-hant/quali/reciprocal_agreement/</a><br />\n<br />\n如今香港政治凌駕專業，咁多工程超資造價已經見到工程師學會已經毫無專業可言，世界各地係時候重申考慮係咪仲認受互認協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲好多其他行業例子，例如會計師，測量師，同好多科學以致物料嘅認證機構等等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2252f0d7fa85ac709eed6c22eff160898ea9b96f","tid":2038783,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74392aee686c2be1896aea8efec5bf8908a9025c","tid":2038783,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e913fca38399821f62458b4e20e05513d9b49c1","tid":2038783,"uid":333223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"你唔好戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，移民都走唔到呀咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}